snippet.title: R-Type Final 3 Evolved - Teaser Trailer (PS5)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/games/r-type-final-2

Enhance, evolve, and eviscerate in R-Type Final 3 Evolved! The legendary side-scrolling shoot-'em-up series makes its way onto PS5™ with classic R-Type gameplay, new features, and more content than ever before.

Coming Spring 2023 to PS5!

#RType #RTypeFinal3Evolved
